(281,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,11,'<p><strong>The Magic Mirror</strong>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In a small village, there lived a young woman named Elara who was known for her kindness. One day, she found an old mirror in the attic. This was no ordinary mirror; it showed the true nature of anyone who looked into it. The village was plagued by a series of thefts, and Elara decided to use the mirror to find the culprit. When the mayor looked into the mirror, it revealed his greedy heart and his involvement in the thefts. He was arrested, and the village was finally at peace.</p>',0,'<p>What is the main theme of this narrative?</p>','','','','<p>The importance of wealth.</p>','<p>The power of honesty.</p>','<p>The danger of magic</p>','<p>The beauty of nature</p>','<p>The value of friendship</p>','','','','','',2,'Y','Y'),
(282,'BING_XII','BIng','G',3,12,'',11,'What does the magic mirror symbolize?','','','','Physical beauty.','Inner truth','Magical powers','Material wealth','Social status','','','','','',2,'Y','Y'),
(283,'BING_XII','BIng','G',1,13,'',11,'What is the resolution of the story?','','','','Elara becomes rich.','The mayor is arrested','The mirror is destroyed','The village is flooded','Elara leaves the village','','','','','',3,'Y','Y'),
(284,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,14,'<p><img class=\"image_resized\" style=\"aspect-ratio:392/220;width:34.59%;\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"392\" height=\"220\"></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Legend tells of Eldoria, a city of great knowledge and magic, lost to time. Archaeologist Dr. Anya Sharma dedicated her life to finding this city. After years of research, she discovered an ancient map leading to a hidden jungle. Following the map, she faced treacherous terrains and ancient traps. Finally, she found the ruins of Eldoria, uncovering its secrets and bringing its history back to light.</p>',0,'<p>What action initiates Dr. Anya Sharma\'s quest?</p>','','','','<p>She finds the ruins of Eldoria</p>','<p>She discovers an ancient map</p>','<p>She faces treacherous terrains</p>','<p>She dedicates her life to finding Eldoria.</p>','<p>She uncovers Eldoria\'s secrets</p>','','','','','',4,'Y','Y'),
(285,'BING_XII','BIng','G',3,15,'',14,'What is the outcome of Dr. Anya Sharma\'s journey?','','Gambar ada di DOC','','She gets lost in the jungle','She gets lost in the jungle','She finds the ruins of Eldoria.','She becomes rich and famous','She faces more ancient traps','','','','','',3,'Y','Y'),
(286,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,16,'<p><strong>Why Students Should Wear Uniforms&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">School uniforms should be mandatory for all students. They promote equality, reduce distractions, and enhance school safety. Firstly, uniforms eliminate socioeconomic disparities, ensuring that all students look the same regardless of their financial background. Secondly, uniforms minimize distractions caused by fashionable clothing, allowing students to focus on their studies. Finally, uniforms make it easier to identify intruders, improving overall school security. For these reasons, uniforms are essential for creating a positive learning environment.</p>',0,'<p>What is the thesis statement of this text?</p>','','','','<p>School uniforms are expensive</p>','<p>Students should express their individuality through clothing.</p>','<p>School uniforms should be mandatory for all students.</p>','<p>Fashionable clothing is a distraction</p>','<p>School safety is not a concern</p>','','','','','',3,'Y','Y'),
(287,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,17,'',16,'What is the generic structure of this text?','','','','Description - Interpretation - Conclusion',' Orientation - Complication - Resolution.','Introduction - Body - Conclusion','Exposition - Climax - Falling Action','Thesis - Arguments - Reiteration','','','','','',5,'Y','Y'),
(288,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,18,'<p><img class=\"image_resized\" style=\"aspect-ratio:332/220;width:36.21%;\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"332\" height=\"220\"></p>',0,'<p>What is the implicit argument presented in the image?</p>','','','','<p>Plastic waste is a major threat to marine life.</p>','<p>Plastic waste has no impact on the environment</p>','<p>Recycling plastic is unnecessary.</p>','<p>Marine animals thrive in plastic waste</p>','<p>Beaches are the best places to dump plastic</p>','','','','','',1,'Y','Y'),
(289,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,19,'',18,'What does the image imply about human responsibility?','','','','Humans have no responsibility for environmental issues','Humans should take responsibility for reducing plastic waste.','Environmental issues are solely the responsibility of governments','Marine animals should adapt to plastic waste','Plastic waste is a natural phenomenon','','','','','',2,'Y','Y'),
(290,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,20,'',18,'Which communication skill is most important when delivering an analytical exposition?','','','','Yelling','Whispering','Using big words','Speaking clearly and confidently.','Speaking very fast','','','','','',4,'Y','Y'),
(291,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,21,'<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The digital age has brought about numerous benefits, but it has also introduced a range of challenges, particularly concerning digital safety. One of the most pressing issues is the prevalence of cyberbullying. With the anonymity provided by the internet, individuals can easily harass and intimidate others without facing immediate consequences. This can lead to severe emotional distress and even mental health problems for the victims.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Furthermore, the spread of misinformation and fake news has become a significant concern. Social media platforms, while providing a space for communication and information sharing, have also become breeding grounds for false narratives. This can manipulate public opinion and create widespread confusion.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Another critical aspect of digital safety is the protection of personal data. With the increasing use of online services, individuals are constantly sharing their personal information. This data can be vulnerable to breaches and misuse, leading to identity theft and financial fraud.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In conclusion, it is imperative that we take digital safety seriously. Education and awareness are key to combating these issues. We must teach young people about responsible online behavior and critical thinking skills to discern credible information. Additionally, stronger regulations and enforcement are needed to protect individuals from cyberbullying and data breaches.</p>',0,'<p>What is the main argument presented in the text?</p>','','','','<p>The benefits of the digital age outweigh the risks.</p>','<p>Digital safety is a minor concern in today\'s society.</p>','<p>Cyberbullying is the only significant problem in digital safety</p>','<p>Social media is entirely harmful and should be avoided.</p>','<p>Digital safety is a critical issue that requires attention</p>','','','','','',5,'Y','Y'),
(292,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,22,'',21,'According to the text, what is a significant consequence of cyberbullying?','','','','Decreased academic performance','Physical injury.','Loss of social media accounts','Physical injury','Emotional distress and mental health problems.','','','','','',5,'Y','Y'),
(293,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,23,'',21,'What does the text suggest about the role of social media in spreading misinformation?','','','','Social media platforms effectively filter out fake news.','Social media can be a breeding ground for false narratives','Social media is the primary source of reliable information.','Social media has no impact on the spread of misinformation.','Social media is only used by credible news outlets.','','','','','',2,'Y','Y'),
(294,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,24,'',21,'Why is the protection of personal data considered a critical aspect of digital safety?','','','',' Personal data is not valuable to anyone.','Data breaches are rare and inconsequential.','Personal data can be misused, leading to identity theft and fraud','Online services do not collect personal data.','Personal data is always encrypted and secure.','','','','','',3,'Y','Y'),
(295,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,25,'',21,'What measures does the text recommend to improve digital safety?','','','','Education, awareness, stronger regulations, and enforcement.',' Ignoring the issues and hoping they resolve themselves.','Relying solely on technology to solve the problems.','Encouraging complete anonymity online.','Limiting internet access for everyone.','','','','','',1,'Y','Y'),
(296,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,26,'<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Illegal fishing, a clandestine operation that disregards national and international regulations, poses a severe threat to marine ecosystems and global food security. These illicit activities, often conducted under the cover of darkness, involve the use of destructive fishing practices, such as trawling and dynamite fishing, which devastate coral reefs and other vital habitats. Furthermore, illegal fishing depletes fish stocks, leading to long-term economic losses for coastal communities that rely on sustainable fishing practices.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">One of the most concerning aspects of illegal fishing is its impact on biodiversity. Many endangered species, including sea turtles and marine mammals, are caught as bycatch in illegal fishing operations. This not only threatens these species but also disrupts the delicate balance of marine ecosystems.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Moreover, illegal fishing undermines efforts to manage fisheries sustainably. By circumventing regulations and quotas, illegal fishing operators contribute to overfishing, which can lead to the collapse of entire fish populations. This has far-reaching consequences for food security, particularly in developing countries where fish is a primary source of protein.</p>',0,'<p>What is the primary impact of illegal fishing on marine ecosystems?</p>','','','','<p>Increased fish population.</p>','<p>Destruction of vital habitats.</p>','<p>Preservation of coral reefs</p>','<p>Enhanced biodiversity.</p>','<p>Improved water quality.</p>','','','','','',2,'Y','Y'),
(297,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,27,'',26,'How does illegal fishing affect endangered species?','','','','It has no impact on them.','It helps increase their population','It protects them from natural predators.','It often results in them being caught as bycatch.','It improves their breeding habitats.','','','','','',4,'Y','Y'),
(298,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,28,'',26,'What is a significant economic consequence of illegal fishing?','','','','Growth of local fish markets','Reduced need for sustainable fishing practices.','Stable fish prices','Long-term economic losses for coastal communities.','Increased profits for all fishing communities.','','','','','',4,'Y','Y'),
(299,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,29,'<p><strong>The Necessity of Implementing Stricter Traffic Laws&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Traffic congestion and accidents are increasing in urban areas. Stricter traffic laws are necessary to address these issues. This would improve road safety, reduce pollution, and enhance overall quality of life. Implementing stricter laws requires consistent enforcement and public awareness campaigns.</p>',0,'<p>What is the main issue discussed in this text?</p>','','','','<p>The advantages of cycling</p>','<p>The importance of road construction.</p>','<p>The need for stricter traffic laws.</p>','<p>The benefits of car ownership.</p>','<p>The cost of public transportation.</p>','','','','','',3,'Y','Y'),
(300,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,30,'',29,'What are the anticipated benefits of stricter traffic laws?','','','','Reduced public transportation usage','Improved road safety and reduced pollution.','Increased traffic congestion.',' Lower quality of life.','Higher pollution levels.','','','','','',2,'Y','Y'),
(301,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,31,'',29,'What is the overall goal of implementing stricter traffic laws?','','','','To increase car sales.','To reduce public transportation usage.','To promote urban sprawl.','To enhance overall quality of life.','To discourage road construction','','','','','',4,'Y','Y'),
(302,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,32,'',29,'What is required for the successful implementation of stricter traffic laws?','','','','No changes in road infrastructure','Minimal government involvement.','Consistent enforcement and public awareness campaigns.','No changes in road infrastructure','Reduced public awareness.','','','','','',3,'Y','Y'),
(303,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,33,'<p><strong>The Ethics of Artificial Intelligence (AI)&nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">The rapid advancement of AI has sparked debates about its ethical implications. Proponents highlight its potential to improve efficiency and solve complex problems. However, opponents express concerns about job displacement, privacy violations, and the potential for AI to be used for harmful purposes. The discussion revolves around balancing the benefits of AI with the need for ethical guidelines and regulations.</p>',0,'<p>What is the central context of this discussion?</p>','','','','<p>The ethical implications of AI.</p>','<p>The technical aspects of AI</p>','<p>The history of AI development.</p>','<p>The economic benefits of AI.</p>','<p>The future of AI technology.</p>','','','','','',1,'Y','Y'),
(304,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,34,'',33,'What is the potential impact of AI on the job market?','','','','It will only affect low-skilled jobs.',' It will lead to significant job displacement.','It will create more jobs than it eliminates','It will enhance job security for all workers.','It will only affect low-skilled jobs.','','','','','',2,'Y','Y'),
(305,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,35,'<p><strong>The Pros and Cons of Online Learning&nbsp;</strong></p><p>Online learning has become increasingly popular in recent years. Proponents argue that it offers flexibility, accessibility, and cost-effectiveness. Students can learn at their own pace and access a wide range of resources from anywhere in the world. However, critics point out the lack of face-to-face interaction, which can hinder social development and create feelings of isolation. Additionally, online learning requires strong self-discipline and technical skills, which some students may lack.</p>',0,'<p>What is one advantage of online learning mentioned in the text?</p>','','','','<p>It offers flexibility</p>','<p>It promotes social development</p>','<p>It requires minimal self-discipline</p>','<p>It eliminates the need for technical skills</p>','<p>It is only accessible to a limited audience</p>','','','','','',1,'Y','Y'),
(306,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,36,'',35,'What is one disadvantage of online learning mentioned in the text?','','','',' It is too expensive',' It enhances face-to-face interaction.','It is not accessible from anywhere','It does not require self-discipline','It can lead to feelings of isolation','','','','','',5,'Y','Y'),
(307,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,37,'',35,'What skill is essential for successful online learning?','','','','Social isolation','Strong self-discipline','Poor technical skills','Lack of self-discipline','Limited access to resources.','','','','','',2,'Y','Y'),
(308,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,38,'',35,'What is the main purpose of this discussion text?','','','','To explain how to use online learning platforms','To entertain readers with stories about online learning','To persuade readers to choose online learning','To present both sides of the online learning debate.','To describe the history of online learning','','','','','',4,'Y','Y'),
(309,'BING_XII','BIng','G',2,39,'The Impact of Social Media on Teenagers\n\nSocial media has a significant impact on teenagers. On one hand, it allows them to stay connected with friends and family, access information, and express themselves creatively. On the other hand, it can lead to cyberbullying, addiction, and unrealistic comparisons. Some argue that social media promotes social awareness and activism, while others believe it distracts teenagers from their studies and real-life interactions',0,'What is one positive impact of social media mentioned in the text?','','','','It enhances real-life interactions','It promotes social awareness','It leads to cyberbullying',' It encourages creative expression','It provides access to information.','','','','','',3,'Y','Y'),
