(1152,'KIMIA_XII','KIM','G',1,14,'',0,'<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Suatu sistem kesetimbangan gas memiliki persamaan reaksi:</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2 PQ<sub>2</sub>(g)&nbsp;⇌ &nbsp;P<sub>2</sub>Q<sub>4</sub>(g)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ΔH = +x kJ/mol</strong></p><p>Jika pada sistem kesetimbangan dinaikkan suhunya maka sistem tersebut akan bergeser....</p>','','','','<p>kanan, karena bergeser ke arah jumlah mol yang kecil</p>','<p>kiri, karena bergeser ke arah eksoterm</p>','<p>kiri, karena bergeser ke arah endoterm&nbsp;</p>','<p>kanan, karena bergeser ke arah endoterm</p>','<p>kiri, karena bergeser ke arah jumlah mol yang besar</p>','','','','','',4,'Y','Y'),
(1153,'KIMIA_XII','KIM','G',1,15,'',0,'<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Dalam wadah bervolume 2 liter dimasukkan gas HBr dan terurai menurut reaksi:</p><p><strong>2HBr<sub>(g)</sub>&nbsp;⇄ H<sub>2(g)</sub> + Br<sub>2(g)&nbsp;</sub></strong></p><p>Data yang diperoleh pada saat kesetimbangan sebagai berikut:</p><figure class=\"table\"><table style=\"border-style:none;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-color:windowtext;border-width:1.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt;vertical-align:top;width:2.0cm;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong>[HBr]</strong></p></td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid;border-color:windowtext;border-left-style:none;border-right-style:solid;border-top-style:solid;border-width:1.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt;vertical-align:top;width:53.6pt;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong>[H<sub>2</sub>]</strong></p></td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid;border-color:windowtext;border-left-style:none;border-right-style:solid;border-top-style:solid;border-width:1.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt;vertical-align:top;width:66.9pt;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong>[Br<sub>2</sub>]</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid;border-color:windowtext;border-left-style:solid;border-right-style:solid;border-top-style:none;border-width:1.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt;vertical-align:top;width:2.0cm;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;\">0,04 M</p></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left-style:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-top-style:none;padding:0cm 5.4pt;vertical-align:top;width:53.6pt;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;\">0,08 M</p></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-left-style:none;border-right:1.0pt solid windowtext;border-top-style:none;padding:0cm 5.4pt;vertical-align:top;width:66.9pt;\"><p style=\"text-align:center;\">0,04 M</p></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>Harga tetapan kesetimbangan reaksi tersebut adalah....</p>','','','','<p>1</p>','<p>2</p>','<p>3</p>','<p>4</p>','<p>6</p>','','','','','',2,'Y','Y'),
(1154,'KIMIA_XII','KIM','G',1,16,'',0,'<p>Nilai Kc untuk reaksi kesetimbangan&nbsp; : SO<sub>2(g)</sub>&nbsp; +&nbsp; O<sub>2(g)</sub>&nbsp; ↔ 2 SO<sub>3(g)</sub>&nbsp; adalah 25.&nbsp;<br>Pada kondisi yang sama, nilai Kc untuk reaksi :&nbsp;<br>SO<sub>3(g)</sub>&nbsp; ↔&nbsp;<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"26\" height=\"20\">&nbsp;O<sub>2(g)</sub> +&nbsp;SO<sub>2(g)</sub>&nbsp; adalah …</p>','','','','<p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"7\" height=\"28\"></p>','<p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"7\" height=\"28\"></p>','<p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"7\" height=\"28\"></p>','<p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"7\" height=\"28\"></p>','<p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"13\" height=\"28\"></p>','','','','','',5,'Y','Y'),
(1155,'KIMIA_XII','KIM','G',1,17,'',0,'<p>Berikut 3 buah persamaan reaksi asam dan basa.<br><strong>&nbsp;</strong>(1)&nbsp;Ca(OH)<sub>2</sub> &nbsp;→ Ca<sup>2+</sup> + 2OH<sup>-</sup><br>&nbsp;(2)&nbsp;H<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup>(aq) + NH<sub>3</sub>(aq) ⇌ NH<sub>4</sub><sup>+</sup>(aq) + H<sub>2</sub>O(aq)<br>&nbsp;(3)&nbsp;NH<sub>3</sub>(aq) + H<sup>+</sup>(aq) → NH<sub>4</sub><sup>+</sup>(aq)<br>Persamaan reaksi asam-basa yang sesuai dengan urutan konsep Arrhenius, Bronsted-Lowry, dan Lewis adalah ....</p>','','','','<p>(3),(2),(1)</p>','<p>(3),(1),(2)</p>','<p>(2),(3),(1)</p>','<p>(2),(1),(3)</p>','<p>(1),(2),(3)</p>','','','','','',5,'Y','Y'),
