(1170,'KIMIA_XII','KIM','G',1,32,'',0,'<p>Jika diketahui :</p><p>Zn<sub>(s)</sub>&nbsp;+&nbsp; Cu<sup>2+</sup><sub>(aq)</sub>&nbsp; →&nbsp; Zn<sup>2+</sup><sub>(aq)</sub>&nbsp; + Cu<sub>(s)</sub>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; E<sup>o</sup>= 1,1 volt</p><p>Sn<sup>2+</sup><sub>(aq)</sub>&nbsp; + 2<i>e&nbsp;</i>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;→&nbsp; Sn<sub>(s)</sub>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;E<sup>o</sup>= -0,14 volt&nbsp;</p><p>Cu<sup>2+</sup><sub>(aq)</sub>&nbsp; + 2<i>e&nbsp;</i>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;→&nbsp; Cu<sub>(s)</sub>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; E<sup>o</sup>= +0,34 volt&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>Maka potensial sel untuk Zn I&nbsp; Zn<sup>2+</sup>&nbsp; II&nbsp; Sn<sup>2+</sup> I Sn, adalah ….</p>','','','','<p>+1,44 volt</p>','<p>+1,24 volt</p>','<p>+0,96 volt</p>','<p>+0,76 volt</p>','<p>+0,62 volt</p>','','','','','',5,'Y','Y'),
(1171,'KIMIA_XII','KIM','G',1,33,'',0,'<p>Beberapa metode pencegahan korosi dalam kehidupan sehari-hari sebagai berikut :</p><ol><li>Pengecatan</li><li>Melumuri dengan oli</li><li>Pembalutan dengan plastik</li><li>Pembalutan dengan timah</li><li>Pelapisan dengan kromium</li></ol><p>Metode yang tepat untuk mencegah korosi pada kaleng makanan dan minuman ditunjukkan dengan angka ….</p>','','','','<p>1</p>','<p>2</p>','<p>3</p>','<p>4</p>','<p>5</p>','','','','','',4,'Y','Y'),
